properties.garden_comments: Property Owner: Recreation and Park DepartmentNo waiting list Opportunities for gardening available. This urban farm has no individual plots, but is managed as a collective, with garden beds cared for by a team of volunteers. Regular workdays are the 1st and 3rd Sundays of the month and the 2nd and 4th Saturdays, Noon to 5 PM. Plus every Monday, 1 PM to 5 PM. At the end of each workday, volunteers get to take produce home. The Farm also regularly hosts field trips and workshops and sponsors a low-income Community Supported Agriculture (CSA) program. www.alemanyfarm.org/Record last updated 11/20/09
